                        <item xml:id="a2">
                           <locus target="#00" n="#">Fol. 17va-vb: Donation note.</locus>
                           <q xml:lang="gez">Fol. 17va-vb: ዝንቱ፡ መጽሐፍ፡ ለመምህር፡ አስካለ፡ ማርያም፡ ወልዱ፡ ለአቡነ፡ ወልደ፡ ዓቢየእግዚእ፡ ዘአስረፀ፡ አክናፈ፡ ከመ፡ መላእክት፡ ዘርእዮ፡ ግኁስ፡ ባህታዊ፡ በዋልባ፡ ወወሀቦ፡ ለመቅደሰ፡ አቡነ፡ አረጋዊ፡ ከመ፡ ይኩኖ፡ መድኀኒተ፡ ሥጋ፡ ወነፍስ፡ ወእኁሁ፡ አባ፡ ገብረ፡ ኢየሱስ፡ ወለወልዱ፡ ተክለ፡ (vb) ማርያም፤ ኦአበውየ፡ ወአኃውየ፡ ኢትርስዑነ፡ ፩፩፡ አቡነ፡ ዘበሰማያት፡ በጊዜ፡ ቅዳሴ፡ ወጸሎት፡ ካህናተ፡ ደም፡ ልዕልት፡ ዳግሚት፡ ሰማይ፡ ማኅደረ፡ ትጉሃን፡ መላእክት፡ ዘኃረያ፡ አረጋዊ፡ ጸባዖት፡ በስብሐት፡ ወበውዳሴ፡ ኅጽርት፨</q>
                           <q xml:lang="en">[Fol. 17va-vb]: This book (belongs) to mämhər ˀAskalä Maryam, son of ˀabunä Wäldä ˁAbiyä ˀƎgziˀ, who spread out (his) wings like angels, which was seen by a secluded hermit in Wal(də)bba, and (who) donated it to the sanctuary of ˀabunä ˀArägawi, so that it may be for him the salvation of (his) body and soul; and (to) his brother ˀabba Gäbrä ˀIyäsus, and to his son Täklä Maryam. Oh my fathers and my brothers, do not forget us, each one (of you say) Paternoster at the time of the Mass and the prayer – (you) priests of Dammo, the exalted, the second heaven, the abode of the watchful angels, which ˀArägawi has chosen, fenced off (by angelic) hosts, by praise and by laudation.</q>
                           <p part="N"/>
                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="e1">- Fol. 1r: The name of the work in written in large letters: 4ቱ ወንጌል. The number of the Ms. according to the monastic library's numbering is written in bottom right corner of the folio.&#xD;
- Fol. 5ra: Additional signature under the text.&#xD;
- Fols. 19v, 43r, 46r, 110r, etc. (in the upper margin): Corrections or omitted passages.&#xD;
- Fols. 46r, 185v (in the upper margin): Crude notes.</item>
